390
00:19:53.490 --> 00:19:55.720
needle me.

391
00:19:55.790 --> 00:19:57.690
anything but look at

392
00:19:55.790 --> 00:19:57.690
them damn figures.

393
00:19:59.790 --> 00:20:01.420
I'm sorry. I...

394
00:20:02.530 --> 00:20:03.590
Is it worth it?

395
00:20:05.200 --> 00:20:07.530
I think we're looking at

396
00:20:05.200 --> 00:20:07.530
