457
00:23:40.350 --> 00:23:42.910
Tipper. it's Cass. Let me in.

458
00:23:47.420 --> 00:23:48.620
Tipper!

459
00:23:51.030 --> 00:23:52.960
Tipper!

460
00:23:53.030 --> 00:23:55.090
- Cass.

461
00:23:53.030 --> 00:23:55.090
