498
00:24:59.830 --> 00:25:03.630
Too needy.

499
00:24:59.830 --> 00:25:03.630
Sorry about that. mate.

500
00:25:03.700 --> 00:25:07.230
Plenty more fish in the sea.

501
00:25:03.700 --> 00:25:07.230
