536
00:26:09.000 --> 00:26:12.300
- I said it just because it's true.

537
00:26:09.000 --> 00:26:12.300
- It's OK.

538
00:26:12.370 --> 00:26:16.030
I consider myself at war

539
00:26:12.370 --> 00:26:16.030
