556
00:26:49.640 --> 00:26:52.300
- Once in a while.

557
00:26:53.670 --> 00:26:56.370
- You two were an item once. right?

558
00:26:53.670 --> 00:26:56.370
- Right.

559
00:26:56.440 --> 00:26:58.140
Much better off now.

560
00:26:58.210 --> 00:27:00.910
