889
00:42:06.490 --> 00:42:08.680
We are weak. we are mortal.

890
00:42:08.760 --> 00:42:12.120
We cannot bend the universe

891
00:42:08.760 --> 00:42:12.120
to our will.

892
00:42:12.190 --> 00:42:14.790
Only when we learn to live

893
00:42:12.190 --> 00:42:14.790
