969
00:49:14.350 --> 00:49:15.750
The building came down on him.

970
00:49:15.820 --> 00:49:16.940
Family?

971
00:49:17.020 --> 00:49:18.990
Yes.

972
00:49:19.050 --> 00:49:20.880
I'll go and talk to them.

973
00:49:20.950 --> 00:49:24.050
They managed to bring

974
00:49:20.950 --> 00:49:24.050
