1010
00:50:34.990 --> 00:50:37.960
Go get your stuff.

1011
00:50:34.990 --> 00:50:37.960
You can go there now if you like.

1012
00:50:38.030 --> 00:50:40.400
- This is your President...

1013
00:50:38.030 --> 00:50:40.400
