1069
00:52:49.160 --> 00:52:50.860
Hey! Shut up and kiss the bride!

1070
00:53:14.950 --> 00:53:16.720
What is it?

1071
00:53:16.790 --> 00:53:18.380
Come with me.

1072
00:53:39.750 --> 00:53:41.610
- Me. Tipper. right?

1073
00:53:39.750 --> 00:53:41.610
