1102
00:56:26.350 --> 00:56:27.780
But I am pleased...

1103
00:56:29.350 --> 00:56:32.810
...that we will be alongside each other.

1104
00:56:38.220 --> 00:56:42.320
I hope we'll achieve great things

1105
00:56:38.220 --> 00:56:42.320
